author: Karoli
title: Jim Webb Said To Be Considering Independent Run For President
text:
sharethis 10/19/15 2:26pm 
The Twitters just lit up with the rumor that Jim Webb is considering a run for President as an independent. Maybe he can coax Donald Trump to join his ticket! 
Here's some of the more hilarious tweets about it. Evidently whatever he decides will be mentioned at the National Press Club tomorrow. It seems the lesson Jim Webb learned from the debate is that he should take steps to avoid appearing in any future debates 
— Ben Jacobs (@Bencjacobs) October 19, 2015 Trump-Webb 2016? 
— David Corn (@DavidCornDC) October 19, 2015 "Jim Webb To Consider Independent Run," per the Webb campaign. pic.twitter.com/RZXh57IdaJ 
— Sahil Kapur (@sahilkapur) October 19, 2015 So Jim Webb basically scammed the Dems into giving him free national airtime to promote his independent run...diabolical 
— Will Bunch (@Will_Bunch) October 19, 2015 @Will_Bunch Also, they say he killed a man once 
— Will Bunch (@Will_Bunch) October 19, 2015 I'm honestly not sure which party's chances (if any) a Jim Webb independent run would be more likely to hurt
